---
import Badge from "../ui/Badge.astro";
import SectionHeading from "../ui/SectionHeading.astro";
import { benefits } from "../../data/benefits.data";
---

<section
  id="nosotros"
  class="bg-coffee-cream pt-12 pb-12 md:pb-18 scroll-m-12"
  aria-labelledby="story-title"
>
  <div class="mx-auto flex flex-col-reverse px-4 md:px-0 md:grid max-w-6xl gap-8 md:gap-16 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="aspect-4/5 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
        <img
          src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB_sIjx1Gw0rEigYy5lApn3QG6h1RDbiGe-8jFG34-VY1asgcr1qb8Ha9JA2i5lY33RZsrkwjf_g-cSCfVjQCgdHZmXtcg3N8z1evwas8NHI8rBmp9m6q6yB3h5dmmBWlMTzD19w77nxLqey3mx2ABAAmscsO6Mv2nco6mK18r2rw7FAqG4dw3yv8Wf3TMRilr74emmUvIqO_mgiTEVs1nZGdJuL6CRq008qI9qWqW6SPEL-hi3GMv8xcxksF5edovA1-AXaBKrKA"
          alt="Manos de agricultor sosteniendo cerezas de café"
          class="h-full w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 hidden rounded-2xl bg-primary p-6 text-center text-secondary shadow-xl lg:block"
      >
        <p class="font-display text-5xl">100%</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Origen directo del <br /> productor</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <SectionHeading
        eyebrow="Nuestra Herencia"
        title="Tradición en cada grano"
        titleTag="h2"
        class="max-w-xl"
      />
      <p id="story-title" class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-secondary/70">
        En La Capilla del Café, no solo servimos una bebida; compartimos el
        esfuerzo de familias caficultoras. Controlamos cada etapa del proceso,
        desde la selección de la semilla en nuestras fincas hasta el tostado
        artesanal.
      </p>

      <nav class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="text-primary"
              ><path
                d="m10 11 11 .9a1 1 0 0 1 .8 1.1l-.665 4.158a1 1 0 0 1-.988.842H20"
              ></path><path d="M16 18h-5"></path><path
                d="M18 5a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v5.573"></path><path
                d="M3 4h8.129a1 1 0 0 1 .99.863L13 11.246"></path><path
                d="M4 11V4"></path><path d="M7 15h.01"></path><path
                d="M8 10.1V4"></path><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="2"
              ></circle><circle cx="7" cy="15" r="5"></circle></svg
            >
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-lg">Cultivo Responsable</h4>
            <p class="text-sm font-light text-black">
              Cosecha manual selectiva en nuestras fincas aliadas.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="text-primary"
              ><path
                d="M12 2c1 3 2.5 3.5 3.5 4.5A5 5 0 0 1 17 10a5 5 0 1 1-10 0c0-.3 0-.6.1-.9a2 2 0 1 0 3.3-2C8 4.5 11 2 12 2Z"
              ></path><path d="m5 22 14-4"></path><path d="m5 18 14 4"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-lg">Tostado de Perfil</h4>
            <p class="text-sm font-light text-black">
              Tostamos en lotes pequeños para resaltar notas únicas.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="text-primary"
              ><path d="M10 2v2"></path><path d="M14 2v2"></path><path
                d="M16 8a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v8a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H7a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V9a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h14a4 4 0 1 1 0 8h-1"
              ></path><path d="M6 2v2"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-lg">Preparación Experta</h4>
            <p class="text-sm font-light text-black">
              Baristas certificados dominando cada método de extracción.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
